140
00:19:35,973 --> 00:19:37,088
MARTIN:
Wow.

141
00:19:38,653 --> 00:19:39,881
Whee!

142
00:19:42,773 --> 00:19:43,967
So do you like it?

143
00:19:46,453 --> 00:19:47,602
Yes.

144
