649
01:10:58,499 --> 01:11:00,535
It's a secret word.

650
01:11:41,579 --> 01:11:43,729
Do you remember this room, Martin?

651
01:11:43,939 --> 01:11:46,248
This is where you were born
the first time.

652
01:11:46,499 --> 01:11:50,731
It's proper that this is the place
for your rebirth, don't you think?

653
01:11:51,819 --> 01:11:54,538
You're growing so quickly, my boy.

654
01:11:57,379 --> 01:11:59,097
Any prediction how soon?

655
01:12:00,419 --> 01:12:02,296
I'd say at least a week.

656
01:12:05,419 --> 01:12:06,738
Martin. . .

657
01:12:08,099 --> 01:12:09,737
. . .if you can hear me. . .

658
01:12:10,299 --> 01:12:13,735
. . .I wanted to tell you
I'm thrilled to have you back.

659
01:12:14,299 --> 01:12:16,369
How it was naughty of you to run away.

660
01:12:17,099 --> 01:12:18,088
I forgive you.

661
01:12:20,739 --> 01:12:22,138
I should thank you. . .

662
01:12:23,139 --> 01:12:25,972
. . .for the magic you worked
with my telepods.

663
01:12:26,819 --> 01:12:29,128
Don't ever forget that, Martin.

664
01:12:29,699 --> 01:12:33,009
You're a magician,
not an escape artist.

665
01:12:34,939 --> 01:12:36,930
Welcome home, son.

666
01:12:37,699 --> 01:12:41,135
Nothing's wrong with me, you assholes!

667
01:12:41,339 --> 01:12:43,330
Let me go!

668
01:12:44,419 --> 01:12:46,535
Where's Martin?

669
01:12:47,499 --> 01:12:49,933
Where's Martin?

670
01:12:50,219 --> 01:12:52,574
It's dirty work, Mackenzie,
but somebody's gotta do it.

671
01:12:52,819 --> 01:12:54,730
Make sure you don't miss anything.

672
01:13:00,699 --> 01:13:04,612
You'll be pleased to know you
show no signs of contamination.

673
01:13:05,099 --> 01:13:06,930
Please, sit down.

674
01:13:11,219 --> 01:13:12,937
You really have no choice.

675
01:13:14,699 --> 01:13:15,973
Where is Martin?

676
01:13:16,219 --> 01:13:18,528
He's doing very, very well.
Thank you.

677
01:13:18,779 --> 01:13:20,531
Resting comfortably.

678
01:13:20,939 --> 01:13:23,533
But of more importance right now. . .

679
01:13:23,939 --> 01:13:26,134
. . .is you telling me. . .

680
01:13:28,219 --> 01:13:30,130
. . .the magic word.

681
01:13:51,139 --> 01:13:53,937
(MACHINE BEEPS)

682
01:14:57,299 --> 01:14:59,290
(MARTIN GURGLES)

683
01:15:55,659 --> 01:15:58,048
(MACHINE BEEPS)

684
01:16:45,939 --> 01:16:46,928
(SCREAMS)

685
01:17:09,379 --> 01:17:11,335
Dr. Jainway?

686
01:18:03,019 --> 01:18:05,692
(SHEPARD SCREAMS)

687
01:18:09,819 --> 01:18:10,808
SCORBY:
Dr. Shepard?

688
01:18:12,739 --> 01:18:13,774
What's wrong?

689
01:18:14,019 --> 01:18:16,010
What's happening, man?
What is it?

690
01:18:16,219 --> 01:18:18,335
Back in the O.R.

691
01:18:22,539 --> 01:18:25,736
You were alone with him all that time,
just you and he.

692
01:18:25,939 --> 01:18:27,930
He must've told you something.

693
01:18:28,179 --> 01:18:31,569
You have no intention of helping
Martin, and you never did.

694
01:18:34,819 --> 01:18:37,731
You're not going anywhere.
Vargas.

695
01:18:38,979 --> 01:18:42,574
Bartok, Martin got out of his
cocoon. He's out there somewhere.

696
01:18:42,819 --> 01:18:44,457
-Has anyone seen him?
-Yeah.

697
01:18:44,699 --> 01:18:47,133
Dr. Jainway. She's dead.
He killed her.

698
01:18:48,219 --> 01:18:50,779
Control, this is Bartok.
Listen carefully.

699
01:18:51,019 --> 01:18:54,568
I do not under any circumstances
want Martin injured or killed.

700
01:18:54,819 --> 01:18:56,093
He is to be contained.

701
01:18:56,739 --> 01:19:00,254
Anyone responsible for damage to him
will answer to me. Is that clear?

702
01:19:00,499 --> 01:19:02,171
Yes, sir. Code four alert.

703
01:19:02,619 --> 01:19:05,656
Code four unit,
quarters 12, 14 and 17.

704
01:19:05,899 --> 01:19:07,537
Subject is dangerous.

705
01:19:07,739 --> 01:19:09,650
All zone four units to be armed.

706
01:19:09,899 --> 01:19:12,459
This is to be a live capture.
Repeat, live capture.

707
01:19:29,619 --> 01:19:33,658
Control, at the end of corridor A,
something's moving around down there.

708
01:19:33,859 --> 01:19:36,532
