712
01:21:04,819 --> 01:21:07,492
(CLATTERING)

713
01:21:56,419 --> 01:21:58,569
-Has anyone found him?
-Not yet.

714
01:21:58,819 --> 01:22:01,094
We're not exactly sure
what he looks like.

715
01:22:02,099 --> 01:22:04,818
Hold it. You wouldn't believe
what I'm looking at, sir.

716
01:22:05,019 --> 01:22:06,975
Whatever it is,
it's dragging a body.

717
01:22:07,419 --> 01:22:09,535
What direction is it headed?

718
01:22:10,419 --> 01:22:14,014
I'd have to say, Mr. Bartok,
it's headed right in your direction.

719
01:22:16,139 --> 01:22:17,128
