Come on, freak.

728
01:24:13,819 --> 01:24:15,537
Shit!

729
01:24:18,899 --> 01:24:22,335
Sorry guys, looks like I lost him.

730
01:24:22,619 --> 01:24:24,735
There's no sign of him anywhere.

731
01:24:28,419 --> 01:24:30,887
