735
01:24:50,979 --> 01:24:52,537
Vargas, let's get him.

736
01:25:20,699 --> 01:25:23,213
-Jesus, look at that.
-Dispatch.

737
01:25:24,219 --> 01:25:27,291
Medical emergency, Bay 1 7.
I got two men down.

738
01:25:27,499 --> 01:25:29,012
I'm going after it.

739
01:25:29,259 --> 01:25:31,932
Paul stay with him.
The rest of you let's go. Come on!

740
01:25:43,659 --> 01:25:46,617
-Just tell them to kill it.
-Don't be an idiot.

741
01:25:46,979 --> 01:25:49,732
I need a live subject.
Martin is of no use dead.

742
