749
01:26:25,419 --> 01:26:29,128
Bay 1 7, observation level.

750
01:26:37,739 --> 01:26:39,331
BETH:
Martin.

751
01:26:45,739 --> 01:26:47,775
-Don't shoot, idiot!
-Kill the damn thing.

752
01:26:47,979 --> 01:26:48,934
-No!
-No!

