758
01:29:30,139 --> 01:29:32,778
We're outside Bay 1 7,
we're cutting in.

759
01:29:37,379 --> 01:29:38,368
WILEY:
Spray the room.

760
01:29:48,379 --> 01:29:49,414
Fuck.

761
